    {
      "id": "cacheHdr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 218,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "💰 Caching vs Compute Cost",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "cacheBody",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 243,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "Compute every request:\n  High CPU → expensive at scale\n\nRedis cache (in-memory):\n  ~$0.01/GB-hr → cheapest hot cache\n  1ms reads vs 20ms DB reads\n\nCDN cache:\n  Bandwidth ~$0.01/GB vs EC2 $0.09/GB\n  → 9x cheaper for static content\n\nRule: read:write > 100:1 → cache it",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "opacity": 100
    },
